    narr:generatedFrom "2919afa61103b9cf74616583515313466d4ad320" ;
    narr:narration """The positioning of aswritten has evolved through several distinct reframes, traceable across dated sessions. The foundational category claim — [expertise installation as a third era of knowledge distribution](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_TrustedInformationEra), after books and search — was established in March 2026 and remains load-bearing. Built on this is the [perspective-vs-information distinction](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_PerspectiveVsInformation): modules install how to interpret information, not just information itself, differentiating the product from RAG. The [steering-as-central-frame](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_SteeringDecisionProcess) (May 2026) positioned aswritten as the memory recurring decision bodies run on — with [governance explicitly rejected](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_GovernanceGraveyardQuote) as a graveyard category. Market targeting moved from enterprise to [SMB primary](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_SMBPrimaryMarket) (March 12) and then to [B2C primary](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_B2CPivot) (March 17), with the [tier-continuum resolution](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_TierContinuumNotDistinctMarkets) (May 2026) reconciling apparent tension: expert, team, and org are one use case varying only by how many people write to and read from the perspective. The go-to-market inverted via [consulting-as-infrastructure](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ConsultingIsMeUsingProduct): the client never touches the tool. Recent additions include the [CEO context-server reframe](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_CEOContextServerReframe) (July 2026), the [anti-monoculture amplifier](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_AntiMonocultureAmplifier) thesis, the [profile-successor framing](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ProfileSuccessorPerspective), and the [individually owned AGI reclaim](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_IndividuationCurveConversionMechanic) with its own-by-default conversion mechanic. The [bounded-domain fidelity argument](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_BoundedDomainFidelityArgument) supports leading with expertise modules over org memory. A [transcript bootstrapping insight](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_TranscriptBootstrappingUnderplayed) (April 2026) was subsequently qualified by [three demotions](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_TranscriptDemotionFrictionNotValue) (July 2026): transcripts lead the onramp, pain leads the value story.""" ;
